HEADWORD: Sasin
<hw>Sa"sin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
Indian antelope (<spn>Antilope bezoartica</spn> syn. <spn>Antilope
cervicapra</spn>), noted for its beauty and swiftness. It has long,
spiral, divergent horns.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

